      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><strong class=\"lead\">Info: </strong>All Liferay Portal 6.x EE versions have reached<a href=\"http://www.liferay.com/subscription-services/end-of-life/liferay-portal\"> End of Service Life</a>.</div>\n\n<p>Use the chart below as well as the definitions that follow to better understand how we provide fixes for our various products.</p>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 697px; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Portal</span></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\"><font size=\"2\">Marketplace Apps</font></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\"><font size=\"2\">Other Products*</font></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">New Release</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><font size=\"2\">Emergency Fix</font></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #28a745; font-size: 1.2em;\">✔</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Fix Packs</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Consolidated Fix Packs</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-cell-expand\" style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"table-cell-expand\" style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><br>\n*Other Products includes Liferay Maven, Liferay Sync, Liferay Developer Studio, Liferay Mobile SDK and Liferay Faces.</p>\n\n<div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content  portlet-draggable yui3-dd-drop yui3-dd-draggable\" id=\"p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_qkRXNFDVv4ZY_\">\n<div class=\"portlet-body\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1411\">\n<div class=\"portlet-borderless-container\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1410\">\n<div class=\"portlet-body\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1409\">\n<div class=\"journal-content-article\" id=\"article_1_3133562_26818917_1.7\">\n<article id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1408\">\n<h2 class=\"section-heading\" id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1407\">New Release</h2>\n\n<p>For each Liferay product, Liferay Subscription Services will notify our engineers upon the discovery of any unintended behavior. These issues will be fixed in a future release of the product in question, whether that is the portal, a marketplace app, or one of our additional products.</p>\n</article>\n\n<article>\n<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Emergency Fix</h2>\n\n<p>For Liferay Portal as well as Marketplace Apps, Liferay Subscription Services will provide fixes for high-impact issues in the Liferay Portal.</p>\n\n<p>Liferay Portal: For the Liferay Portal, an emergency hotfix will be provided via the Liferay Help Center to patch the issue in question.</p>\n\n<p>Marketplace Apps: For high-impact issues within Liferay Marketplace apps*, Support will go beyond fixing the issue in the latest version and will provide subscribers with an updated version of the app via a Help Center ticket. This version will be complete with all the known fixes for the app to date.</p>\n\n<p>*Excludes Lab Apps</p>\n</article>\n\n<article>\n<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Fix Packs</h2>\n\n<p>Liferay Subscription Services will periodically release fix packs for certain areas of the Liferay Portal. Fix Packs are carefully selected collections of patches that will uphold the quality and reliability of the Portal. Fix packs undergo a rigorous testing and QA phase and thus introduce significantly less risk to the portal than an emergency hot fix.</p>\n</article>\n\n<article>\n<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Consolidated Service Packs</h2>\n\n<p>As fix packs are created over time, Liferay will periodically release consolidated fix packs for the Liferay Portal. As the name implies a consolidated fix pack is essentially a combination of the fix packs to date, comprising fixes across many different areas of the portal. Installing these are the easiest way to keep your portal up-to-date.</p>\n</article>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"entry-links\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content  portlet-draggable yui3-dd-drop\" id=\"p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_yTF3yqXacdql_\"><span id=\"p_56_INSTANCE_yTF3yqXacdql\"></span>\n\n<div class=\"portlet-body\">\n<div class=\"portlet-borderless-container\">\n<div class=\"portlet-body\">\n<div class=\"journal-content-article\" id=\"article_1_3133562_13757522_2.5\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
      },
